title: RHOSLC: The Ice Storm
description: Meredith and Jen finally come face to face on The Real Housewives of Salt Lake City this week, and what better place to have a throw down than on thin ice. This episode brings new meaning to the expression "out like trout."
author: watchwhatcrappens@gmail.com (benron)
